description:
From physics to coding and robotics. This led Miranda's journey to KubeCon + CloudNativeCon, and have experienced firsthand, friendly and supportive community. Join us in Salt Lake City this November for KubeCon + CloudNativeCon 2024 and discover a world of support and learning! 

Learn more: https://events.linuxfoundation.org/kubecon-cloudnativecon-north-america/
